These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
There 3 different types of food: plum, spinach, radish
1. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
2. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person eating spinach##8
3. the person eating radish is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Food   | radish | spinach | plum |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
3 different games are played: poker, canasta, domino
1. the person playing domino is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
2. the person playing domino is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Game   | poker | domino | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | baking | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
