.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, bird
1. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Pet   | frog | goldfish | bird |

