2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |   3   |
| Birthday   | august | october | june |

